%e A102471 Sum_{k=0 to 6} 1/k! = 1957/720 and 720 = 6! = (2*3)!, so 3 is a member. But Sum_{k=0 to 12} 1/k! = 260412269/95800320 and 95800320 < 12! = (2*6)!, so 6 is not a member.
